<item>
            <title>[LU-15157] conf-sanity 21e and 77 can fail when zfs packages are installed but mkfs.lustre is not installed.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15157</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;conf-sanity 21e and 77 can fail when zfs packages are installed but mkfs.lustre is not installed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Such a case looks like the following:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;stdout.log&lt;br/&gt;
 conf-sanity test_77: @@@@@@ FAIL: add fs2ost failed &lt;br/&gt;
  Trace dump:&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/../tests/test-framework.sh:6110:error()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/conf-sanity.sh:5591:test_77()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/../tests/test-framework.sh:6394:run_one()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/../tests/test-framework.sh:6433:run_one_logged()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/../tests/test-framework.sh:6229:run_test()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/conf-sanity.sh:5599:main()&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Dumping lctl log to /tmp/test_logs/1566916655/conf-sanity.test_77.*.1566916718.log&lt;br/&gt;
pdsh@fre0339: fre0339: ssh exited with exit code 2&lt;br/&gt;
pdsh@fre0339: fre0340: ssh exited with exit code 2&lt;br/&gt;
Resetting fail_loc on all nodes...done.&lt;br/&gt;
umount /mnt/lustre2 ...&lt;br/&gt;
umount: /mnt/lustre2: not mounted&lt;br/&gt;
stopping fs2mds ...&lt;br/&gt;
Stopping /mnt/lustre-fs2mds (opts:-f) on fre0337&lt;br/&gt;
stopping fs2ost ...&lt;br/&gt;
FAIL 77 (22s)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
